s founded in  and is a  billion alternative asset management company with headquarters in new york and offices around the world mr edens is responsible for fortress’s private equity business which primarily invests in transportation and infrastructure real estate health care financial services and media prior to founding fortress mr edens was a partner and managing director of blackrock financial management inc where he headed blackrock asset investors a private equity fund in addition mr edens was formerly a partner and managing director of lehman brothers mr edens received a bs in finance from oregon state university bio marc lasry press release related content bucks the greek freak invades manila july   jalen moore summer league highlights july   bronson koenig summer league highlights july   bucks dancers prepare for final audition july   sterling brown summer league highlights july   milwaukee bucks dancers  finalists july   wesley r edens  executive bio compensation history and contacts  equilar atlas   log in  sign up x   as featured in wesley r edens principal and cochairman of the board at fortress investment group llc view full profile are you wesley r edens claim your profile   sign up for equilar atlas and view wesley r edenss full profile with equilar atlas you can identify corporate executives in wesley r edenss network and community follow changes in wesley r edenss employment and moneyinmotion connect with wesley r edens through your network of contacts wesley r edenss executive work history current principal and cochairman of the board fortress investment group llc chairman of the board drive shack inc chairman of the board and director onemain holdings inc chairman of the board new media investment group inc board member intrawest resorts holdings inc chairman of the board new senior investment group inc past to view wesley r edenss complete executive work history sign up now education bs oregon state university age      wesley r edenss biography w