 whistler blackcomb holdings inc from october  to november  prior to forming fortress mr edens was a partner and a managing director of blackrock financial management inc where he headed blackrock asset investors a private equity fund in addition mr edens was formerly a partner and a managing director of lehman brothers mr edens received a bs in finance from oregon state university mr edenss extensive credit private equity finance and management expertise extensive experience as an officer and director of public companies and his deep familiarity with our company led our board of directors to conclude that mr edens should be elected to serve as a director source fortress investment group llc on    sign up for equilar atlas and view wesley r edenss full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like wesley r edens more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in wesley r edenss network and community follow changes in wesley r edenss employment and moneyinmotion connect with wesley r edens through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example wesley r edens wesley r edenss connections  sign up now to view wesley r edenss  connections » ronald w allen board member the cocacola company douglas a hacker board member aircastle limited russell goodman board member metro inc andrew f jacobs former employee and consultant capstead mortgage corporation w benjamin moreland executive vice chairman of the board crown castle international corp ronald l merriman board member pentair plc jordan b savitch former senior vice president and general counsel penn national gaming inc ronald j naples board member penn national gaming inc mark s whiting board member capstead mortgage corporation john v finamore former senior vice president regional operations penn national gaming inc popular profiles sign up now to view more executive profiles » thoma