nd serves on the board of two registered investment companies fortress registered investment trust and fortress investment trust ii he is the chairman of the board of directors and chief executive officer of newcastle investment corp an affiliate of fortress listed on the new york stock exchange he is also chairman of the board of directors of brookdale senior living inc a senior living company listed on the new york stock exchange since its inception in november  and chairman of the board of directors of global signal inc a new york stock exchange listed company since its reorganization in october  and was chief executive officer of global signal inc from february  to april  mr edens is the chairman of the board of directors of aircastle limited and has served in this capacity since october  mr edens is also a director and the chief executive officer of eurocastle investment limited an affiliate of fortress which is currently listed on the euronext amsterdam exchange and chairman of the board of directors of mapeley limited which has been listed on the london stock exchange since june    wesley edens colleagues  name title email michael reed board dir ceo please login paul ameden cio please login bill blevins vp  online operations please login brad dennison vp  content news operations please login scott champion co  pres co  coo  western region please login             home    about us    product information     subscription    list builder     executive list     email lists     contact us    site map    browse directory      �  walkerss research  a publisher of business information since  all rights reserved